Class CoordinateBruteForce<T extends Coordinate>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openimaj.knn.CoordinateBruteForce<T>

    T - the type of Coordinate
    All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class CoordinateBruteForce<T extends Coordinate>
extends Object
implements CoordinateIndex<T>
    Implementation of a CoordinateIndex that performs searching by brute-force comparison over the indexed coordinates.
    Author:
    Jonathon Hare (jsh2@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
